* text=auto

*.cs text
*.shader text
*.shadergraph text
*.mat text
*.prefab text
*.unity text whitespace=-blank-at-eol
*.asset text
*.meta text
*.controller text whitespace=-blank-at-eol
*.anim text
*.asmdef text
*.json text
*.txt text

*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.tif binary
*.tiff binary
*.fbx binary
*.ogg binary
*.mp3 binary
*.wav binary
*.webm binary
*.dll binary

# Unity can serialize these assets in a binary format. Treating them as text
# lets core.autocrlf silently corrupt their byte stream on Windows.
**/LightingData.asset binary
**/NavMesh.asset binary
**/TerrainData*.asset binary
